  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "An ***analogy*** is an extended comparison between two things that are unlike in most respects but similar in the respect that matters for the writer's purpose. Where a metaphor identifies (\"grief is an ocean\"), an analogy explains (\"grief is like an ocean in that it comes in waves — sometimes calm, sometimes overwhelming, and you can't control which\").",
